        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="TNYAdobeCaslonPro, 'Times New Roman', serif;" color="#000000">
          <h2 style="             
              font-size: 24px;
              line-height: 1.2;
              font-weight: 500;
              margin-top: 2px !important;">Trump launches a trade war </h2>
        </mj-text> 
        <mj-image border-radius="10px" padding="10px 12px" width="600px" src="https://www.longandshort.com/email/images/ls-feb-3-1.png" alt="US probes DeepSeek over Nvidia chip access via Singapore" href="https://www.longandshort.com" />
        <mj-text padding="0px 12px" font-family="Roboto+Serif" color="#A9A7AF">
          <p style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.2; color: #A9A7AF;">President Donald Trump talks with Justin Trudeau. Credits: CBC
          </p>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="Roboto+Serif" color="#000000">
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5">US President Donald Trump has initiated a major trade war by <a style="text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 2px solid  #6b705c; color: black;" href="https://link.longandshort.com/ls-03-02-2025-h1-1-imposing-sweeping-tariffs?source=website" target="_blank">imposing sweeping tariffs</a> on imports from Canada, Mexico, and China. The new tariffs now include a 25% tariff on many Canadian and Mexican products, a 10% duty on Canadian energy, and an additional 10% tariff on Chinese goods.</p>
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5">Canada and Mexico have been <a style="text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 2px solid  #6b705c; color: black;" href="https://link.longandshort.com/ls-03-02-2025-h1-2-swift-to-respond?source=website" target="_blank">swift to respond</a> to the imposed tariffs. Both countries are preparing their tariffs on US goods. Canada Premier Justin Trudeau announced 25% tariffs on $155 billion of American products. Mexico has also vowed for countermeasures. China has condemned the measures and said it would file a lawsuit at the World Trade Organization. </p>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-divider border-width="1px" border-style="solid" border-color="lightgrey" padding="10px 12px" />
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
