              line-height: 1.2; 
              font-weight: 500;
              margin-top: 2px !important;">Singapore vows cooperation with US amid DeepSeek concerns</h2>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="Roboto+Serif" color="#000000">
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5;filter:blur(5px);">Singapore has <a style="text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 2px solid  #6b705c; color: black;" href="https://link.longandshort.com/ls-03-02-2025-h2-3-reaffirmed-its-commitment?source=website" target="_blank">reaffirmed its commitment</a> to work with the US authorities as they investigate whether DeepSeek acquired the latest Nvidia chips via Singapore. The country’s Ministry of Trade stated that Nvidia had found no evidence that DeepSeek obtained restricted products through Singapore.
          </p>
          
        </mj-text>
